# API Test Examples

This file contains example HTTP requests for testing the Bank Saving System API.
You can use REST Client extension in VS Code or import to Postman.

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### ========== CUSTOMERS ==========

### Get All Customers
GET http://localhost:3000/api/customers

### Search Customers
GET http://localhost:3000/api/customers?search=john

### Get Customer by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/customers/{{customerId}}

### Create Customer
POST http://localhost:3000/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe"
}

### Update Customer
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/customers/{{customerId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated"
}

### Delete Customer
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/customers/{{customerId}}

### ========== DEPOSITO TYPES ==========

### Get All Deposito Types
GET http://localhost:3000/api/deposito-types

### Get Deposito Type by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/deposito-types/{{depositoTypeId}}

### Create Deposito Type
POST http://localhost:3000/api/deposito-types
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Deposito Platinum",
  "yearly_return": 0.10
}

### Update Deposito Type
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/deposito-types/{{depositoTypeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Deposito Platinum Plus",
  "yearly_return": 0.12
}

### Delete Deposito Type
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/deposito-types/{{depositoTypeId}}

### ========== ACCOUNTS ==========

### Get All Accounts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/accounts

### Get Accounts by Customer
GET http://localhost:3000/api/accounts?customer_id={{customerId}}

### Get Account by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/accounts/{{accountId}}

### Create Account
POST http://localhost:3000/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "{{customerId}}",
  "deposito_type_id": "{{depositoTypeId}}",
  "initial_balance": 1000000
}

### Delete Account
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/accounts/{{accountId}}

### ========== TRANSACTIONS ==========

### Get All Transactions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions

### Get Transactions by Account
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions?account_id={{accountId}}

### Process Deposit
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transactions/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_id": "{{accountId}}",
  "amount": 500000,
  "transaction_date": "2025-12-02T12:00:00Z"
}

### Process Withdrawal
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transactions/withdrawal
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_id": "{{accountId}}",
  "amount": 200000,
  "transaction_date": "2025-12-02T12:00:00Z"
}
